7:["$","article",null,{"className":"min-h-screen bg-white","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12","children":[["$","header",null,{"className":"mb-8","children":[["$","h1",null,{"className":"text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4","children":"Specification to implement ISO 45001 in retail industry in UAE"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"flex items-center gap-4 text-gray-600","children":[["$","time",null,{"dateTime":"2026-01-02T06:30:51+00:00","children":"January 2, 2026"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 rounded-full text-sm","children":"general"}]]}]]}],null,["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-8 p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500","children":["$","p",null,{"className":"text-gray-700 italic","children":"Specification to implement ISO 45001 in retail industry in UAE\n\t\t\t\tEmployee and consumer safety and well-being should be as essential to retail businesses"}]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-lg max-w-none mb-8 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed","children":[["$","p","0",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Specification to implement ISO 45001 in retail industry in UAE"}],["$","p","1",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Employee and consumer safety and well-being should be as essential to retail businesses as they are to other sophisticated company sectors. As a result, it comes to reason that many retail businesses are getting ISO 45001 certified to improve staff and consumer safety and well-being. So, given the increased interest in developing an effective ISO 45001-certified OHSMS (Operational Health and Safety Management System), what should a retail company's objectives be, and what actions should be done to guarantee that the ISO 45001 implementation provides maximum benefit?"}],["$","p","2",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Identifying hazards in the retail sector, UAE"}],["$","p","3",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"A retail manager who wish to get ISO 45001 certification in Dubai, made a short online search that is revealed from the following incidents:"}],["$","p","4",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Slips and falls Employees are injured as a result of risks."}],["$","p","5",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"In some places, there are risks associated with pallet lifts."}],["$","p","6",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Shelf stacking and the dangers of working at heights"}],["$","p","7",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"The threat of an attack or assault by a member of the general public"}],["$","p","8",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"One sad instance in the UK occurred when a little kid was killed in an accident with an interior display at a shop, which may have been defective and is being investigated"}],["$","p","9",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"As a result, it is quite simple to construct a persuasive argument for why all businesses with more than a particular headcount should have an ISO 45001-certified OHSMS in place. So, given that, what advice and recommendations can a retail company use to guarantee that installation is as pleasant as possible and that the OHSMS has the greatest potential impact? This article will go through how to obtain ISO 45001 certification in Dubai in further depth."}],["$","p","10",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"ISO 45001 Certification in the retail sector, UAE"}],["$","p","11",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"The fundamentals must be met by any business adhering to the ISO 45001 standard. A Health and Safety Policy must be developed to address the general limits, dangers, and objectives associated with the organization and its operations. All clauses of the ISO 45001 Certification in Abu Dhabistandard must be met, however it may pay to focus especially on key components that may allow you to extract additional value for your retail business:"}],"$L10","$L11","$L12","$L13","$L14","$L15","$L16","$L17","$L18"]}],"$L19"]}]}]
